init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She calls up one of the guys who has been wooing her, pretending to be a friend of his.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman calls up another man on a date, and has him meet her at the same coffee shop that one of the other men suggested;

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She then begins to test him, to see if he really is a shapeshifter.
